Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ZABOERA'S SCHEME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon your Mystic Legion at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll summon my elite guards as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll gather our remaining forces\Nand launch a mass offensive against Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Lord Hadorra!\NThat plan already failed once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's party cannot be defeated\Nwith any regular tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassination through careful planning\Nwould be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A victor is not one who is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A victor is one who survives\Nto the end by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been using Behoma nonstop\Nto tend to our wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a difficult fight.\NWe're lucky we all survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran may be gone,\Nbut the other Legion Commanders remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't stand a chance\Nif we're attacked now. I'll stand guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't in that condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The half-dead should take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave guard duty to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NIf we're half-dead, you really were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You need rest the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm not sure why,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I actually feel better than\Nbefore I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your bravado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself if it's bravado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a Gira spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible unless\Nyou really focus your Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See? For some reason\NI'm in tip-top shape today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. It looks like\Nyou're in the best shape among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NIf things get ugly, I'll give a shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been said that drinking the legendary\NDragon's blood grants immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Baran's blood has made\NPopp's body stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if you drink my blood\Nwill you all get stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran said\Nyour blood is closer to a human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww. I thought if I had that power,\NI could keep anyone from dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Dai. We won't die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And that includes Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the least I can do to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My suicide attack fails,\Nand I end up saved by my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I won't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to cast Megante again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just meant I won't mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew Popp was forcing himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll survive until the end.\NI promised on the other side, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you our guardian or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't push yourself any further.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Things sound rough. Need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is it... Is it really you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten\Nyour friend's face already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's Maam,\None of the Disciples of Aban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp looks so happy to see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your martial arts training?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all trained up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.\NI packed it in before I finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got worried about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam quit something before completing it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know why, but I don't like her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something sinister about her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodness! I must be just jealous of her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see Dai and Leona and the others!\NThey're in for a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Popp. They're exhausted\Nfrom fighting and asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not wake them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'd like to stay here\Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Something smells sweet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel woozy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I can't believe it.\NMaam would never do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought a friend with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mystic Bishop Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on guard, so I borrowed\NMaam's likeness with a Morph spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told you're quite fond of the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My body contains hundreds of poisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I injected the most potent\Nneurotoxin through my claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up! You can't even scream now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to the Dark Incense\NI've been diffusing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's in a slumber\Ndeeper than the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can assassinate\Nall of them now, Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect this one\Nto resist the Dark Incense, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he's gained some special power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Disciples of Aban for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They gain power when you're not watching\Nand bare their fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should kill him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always cruel,\Nbut you never played dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've fought before, but you always had\Nthe dignity of the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're resorting\Nto the dirty tricks of this old gremlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh how the mighty have fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot fail again! I don't have\Nthe luxury of choosing my methods!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,\NCrocodine once said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, he realized the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more important things\Nthan winning or losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can lecture Lord Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A few more pricks and I'm sure you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your grubby little paws off of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor... Matorif!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.63,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEGIRAMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAT-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.64,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,DARK INCENSE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor... Matorif!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron, you let them trick you.\NYou need to work on your perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, a Mage must always be\Nthe most level-headed in the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when everybody's worked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to stay cool as ice\Nand understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that was what I did\Nwhen working with Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You sided with Aban and resisted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You called yourself\Nthe most powerful human Grand Sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, you seem well,\Nyou third-rate Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't just die\Nso now I have to play clean-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus you killed one of my only friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good guy. He really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wasn't even a third of my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka... Aban... All the good ones die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And crooks like you and me\Nend up surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What an ugly world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you a deal. I'll send you\Nto the afterlife, so go apologize to Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you old fossil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reduce all of you to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama.{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Kiari.{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two spells at once?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not healing right away.\NThey got him with a powerful poison.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begiragon!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begiragon!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can a mere human use Begiragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you had a patent?!\NGet over yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm losing!\NIs his Magic Power greater than mine?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I was younger!\NMy body can't keep up with the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No! My mentor is in danger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate everyone in the shack\Nwill die, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Everyone, wake up! Please wake up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big guy! Hyunckel! Princess! Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you've reached your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're the one\Nwho'll be seeing Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Popp calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone, Hadorra!\NI'll never let another friend die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one more friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He focused all his power into his fist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and reflected their Begirama spells\Nwith his own Begirama spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I can't do that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit them with all that Heat Energy.\NHadorra must be done for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NHe's pretty tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You had to save me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But you know,\NI appreciate what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll never let another friend die."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You softies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we sleep through\Nan explosion of this size?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera and Hadorra showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to get away with a Rura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Those filthy little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt Hadorra survived that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the help I gave him,\Nhe's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ingratiate myself\Nwith Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera, I won't let you betray me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are in the same boat now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try latching on\Nto someone else, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about your secret research\Nabout Superior Beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?!\N-It's time to use that research for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Disciples of Aban\Nare growing fast! Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This body King Ban gave me\Nisn't enough to keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I need greater power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Power like that Dragonoid Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the greatest power in the world\Nbeyond anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That explains\Nthe Crest on your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impressive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry. We fell into a trap\Nby Zaboera of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't beat yourself up over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody even had their feelings\Nmanipulated and got all spoony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Hadorra\Nactually participated in Zaboera's scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always one\Nwho preferred brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably realized\Nbrute force wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it turns out the Hero is the son of\Nthe legendary Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have been pretty desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think something big is going on\Nwithin the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mentor, you knew\NDai is a Dragon Knight, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have told us sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus you could've shown up sooner,\Ncouldn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew learning the fate of the\NDragon Knight would hurt you mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do\Nto help with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured only one person could help,\Nso I dug this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this dirty book... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This mark... Is it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThis is the famous Book of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Aban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban, the Hero who saved the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote of his skills, spells, and thoughts\Nfor future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only hand-written book of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew there was such a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stored in the Library of Carl,\Nhis home country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd need it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the Book of Air, page 192.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Earth is about combat skills.\NSea covers Aura skills and spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Book of Air is of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"To the... and..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, can you read it?\NI can't read a lot of the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"To the wounded and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat is not to fall from your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is when you lose yourself\Nafter falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be strong of heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calmly consider your goals\Nand your abilities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are all limited in what we can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When each of us does the best we can do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:21:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even when on the edge of despair,\Nthe path to victory shall shine through."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost like Master is here\Nreassuring us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those were just the words\Nwe needed to hear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the item\Nfor green little fledglings like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Matorif.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your goals and abilities..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return to Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do the best that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Something more for the world\Nthan just fighting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something only I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:07.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:15.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:19.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:38.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:53.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:08.53,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
